result:
<a-modal
  :title="title"
  :width="800"
  :visible="visible"
  :confirmLoading="confirmLoading"
  @ok="handleOk"
  @cancel="handleCancel"
  cancelText="关闭">
  
  <a-spin :spinning="confirmLoading">
    <a-form :form="form">
    
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="分类ID">
        <a-input-number v-decorator="[ 'catgoryid', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="一级分类ID">
        <a-input-number v-decorator="[ 'fistcatgory', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="二级分类ID">
        <a-input-number v-decorator="[ 'secondcatgory', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="标题">
        <a-input placeholder="请输入标题" v-decorator="['title', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="图标">
        <a-input placeholder="请输入图标" v-decorator="['icon', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="浏览量">
        <a-input-number v-decorator="[ 'viewcount', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="评论数">
        <a-input-number v-decorator="[ 'commentcount', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="类型1纯文字、2纯图片、3纯视频、4纯音频、5图文、6视频与图文、7音频与图文">
        <a-input-number v-decorator="[ 'contenttype', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="内容（纯文字/图文）">
        <a-input placeholder="请输入内容（纯文字/图文）" v-decorator="['content', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="图片（多张以；隔开）">
        <a-input placeholder="请输入图片（多张以；隔开）" v-decorator="['images', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="视频/音频地址">
        <a-input placeholder="请输入视频/音频地址" v-decorator="['videourl', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="视频/音频时长">
        <a-input-number v-decorator="[ 'videotime', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="视频第一针图片">
        <a-input placeholder="请输入视频第一针图片" v-decorator="['videoimage', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="发布时间">
        <a-input placeholder="请输入发布时间" v-decorator="['createtime', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="作者名">
        <a-input placeholder="请输入作者名" v-decorator="['authorname', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="作者ID">
        <a-input-number v-decorator="[ 'authorid', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="作者描述">
        <a-input placeholder="请输入作者描述" v-decorator="['author', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="1、免费；2、会员；3、付费">
        <a-input-number v-decorator="[ 'type', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="付费金额">
        <a-input-number v-decorator="[ 'price', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="是否推荐到分类">
        <a-input-number v-decorator="[ 'iscategoryrecomed', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="是否推荐到首页">
        <a-input-number v-decorator="[ 'isindexrecomend', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="直播间号">
        <a-input-number v-decorator="[ 'roomid', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="聊天室ID">
        <a-input placeholder="请输入聊天室ID" v-decorator="['groupid', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="点赞数">
        <a-input-number v-decorator="[ 'topcount', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="审核状态： 0审核中 1审核成功 2审核失败">
        <a-input-number v-decorator="[ 'status', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="拒绝原因">
        <a-input placeholder="请输入拒绝原因" v-decorator="['refusereason', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        label="是否删除 0否1是">
        <a-input-number v-decorator="[ 'del', {}]" />
      </a-form-item>

    </a-form>
  </a-spin>
</a-modal>
